name: GIG POSTERS BOOK VOL 2.
description:
Gig Posters Volume 2 showcases a spectacular compilation of rock show art by one hundred of today’s most talented designers. 

The book includes a large perforated version (for framing) of my Queens of The Stone Age Dublin ’08 poster and a brief interview. Published by Quirk books/Random House and authored by Clay Hayes, curator of Gigposters.com

I will happily sign this page on request.

* Note - this product ships to the USA ONLY. International orders may be refunded.
